      </simpleChoice>
      <simpleChoice identifier="C1">
        <span>To identify any factors or gaps in knowledge that may have been overlooked in previous research.</span>
      </simpleChoice>
      <simpleChoice identifier="C2">
        <span>To provide a comprehensive bibliography of all the work done on your topic.</span>
      </simpleChoice>
      <simpleChoice identifier="C3">
        <span>To point to general agreements and disagreements between other researchers in your field.</span>
      </simpleChoice>
      <simpleChoice identifier="C4">
        <span>To show why your work has value as a contribution to the literature.</span>
      </simpleChoice>
